---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Tomoya & Rina Wedding Invitation">
    <section
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-screen pb-25
           bg-gradient-to-b from-cream-200 from-55% via-cream-100 via-75% to-white to-90%">

           <img
           src="/images/flower1.png"
           alt=""
           class="mx-auto mt-6 w-[85%] h-auto select-none pointer-events-none"
           loading="eager" decoding="async" />
    <img
      src="/images/title.svg"
      alt="Tomoya & Rina / Wedding Invitation / 2026.1.18  13:10 RECEPTION OPEN"
      class="mx-auto my-6 w-[80%] h-auto"
      loading="eager" decoding="async" />

      <img
      src="/images/flower2.png"
      alt=""
      class="mx-auto w-[88%] h-auto select-none pointer-events-none"
      loading="eager" decoding="async" />
	</section>
  <section class="py-10 text-center">
    <p class="mb-6">謹啓
<br/>
<br/>皆様におかれましては
<br/>ますますご清祥のことと
<br/>お慶び申し上げます
<br/>
<br/>このたび私たちは
<br/>結婚式を挙げることになりました
<br/>つきましては皆様により一層の
<br/>ご指導を賜りたく
<br/>ささやかではございますが披露宴を
<br/>催したく存じます
<br/>
<br/>ご多用中誠に恐縮ではございますが
<br/>ぜひご出席をいただきたく
<br/>ご案内申し上げます
<br/>
<br/>謹白
<br/>
<br/>令和八年一月吉日
<br/>
<br/>古川智也
<br/>荒瀬梨奈</p>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10 text-center flex gap-10 flex-col items-center">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-script">Hosts</h2>
    <div class="flex gap-10 items-center pl-15 text-lg"><div>古川 智也</div> <div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-cream-200"></div></div>
    <div class="flex gap-10 items-center pr-15 text-lg"><div class="h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-cream-200"></div><div>荒瀬梨奈</div></div>
    <div class="flex gap-5 items-center flex-col"><div class="h-33 w-33 rounded-full bg-cream-200"></div><div>アンちゃん</div></div>
  </section>

  <section class="sticky bottom-0 py-5 text-center text-sm bg-gradient-to-b from-white/0 from-0% to-white to-60%">
    <a
    href="https://forms.gle/mjUcVsJjaDKHzYyu7"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class="inline-block bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-white px-8 py-4 mb-3 rounded-full text-lg shadow transition"
  >
    ご出欠の回答フォームへ
  </a>
    <p>© 2025 Tomoya & Rina Wedding Invitation</p>
  </section>
</Base>
